<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>ビスタジア｜ピカイチ投票でサッカーをもっと熱く！</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Noto+Sans+JP">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f6fc;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #114488;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 1rem auto;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
    .match-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 1rem;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }
    .match-card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }
    .teams {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .vote-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #28a745;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .vote-button:hover {
      background-color: #218838;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      color: #555;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    ⚽ ビスタジア ⚽<br>
    <span style="font-size:1rem; font-weight:normal;">サポーターの投票で選手を輝かせよう！</span>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <% matches.forEach(match => { %>
      <div class="match-card">
        <div class="teams">🔥 <%= match.home %> vs <%= match.away %> 🔥</div>
        <div><strong>ピカイチ選手を決めるのはあなた！</strong></div>
        <a href="/match/<%= match.id %>" class="vote-button">📣 投票する！</a>
      </div>
    <% }); %>
  </div>

